---
/* CONTRACT: VIS status snapshot for Article System v0.1 with lightweight follow-up notes. */
import PrototypeLayout from "../../../../layouts/PrototypeLayout.astro";
---

<PrototypeLayout title="Article Changelog">
  <main class="px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 sm:py-8">
    <h1 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Changelog / status</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-prose text-sm text-gray-600">
      Kort statusflate for hva som er landet i v0.1. VIS er fortsatt referansevisning, ikke oppgavestyring.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white p-4">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700">Landed nå</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li>Delte artikkelkomponenter under <code class="font-mono">src/components/article/</code>.</li>
        <li>Delt stylesheet: <code class="font-mono">src/styles/article-system.css</code>.</li>
        <li>Semantiske artikkel-tokens i <code class="font-mono">src/styles/tokens.css</code>.</li>
        <li>Sandbox Article Master rewired til delt system.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-4">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700">Akseptert for nå</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li>Article Master i sandbox er referansemal for v0.1.</li>
        <li>VIS viser orientering for review, ikke redesign eller utforskning.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-white p-4">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700">Pending / next</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li>Token cleanup videreføres i relatert oppfølging (#17).</li>
        <li>Eventuelle nye komponentutvidelser tas i ny iterasjon, ikke i denne VIS-passeringen.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</PrototypeLayout>
